are invited to the 106th FFA monthly interclub practice. This series of
joint monthly practice sessions started in September 2000. The FFA is recognized by Japan Aikikai.<br><br><br>Details:<br>&nbsp;<br>DATE AND TIME:<br>Saturday, 2010 February 06<br>1830 hrs (6:30 p.m.) (Interclub practices always start at this time regardless of venue)<br><br>THIS MONTH'S HOST:<br>Tada-Juku (ACP)<br><br>THIS MONTH'S VENUE:<br>Club 650<br>C-5 Road, Libis, Pasig City*<br><br>ALL REGARDLESS OF ORGANIZATIONAL AFFILIATION ARE WELCOME. For more details, e-mail
<span style="border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(0, 102, 204); cursor: pointer;" class="yshortcuts" id="lw_1263218017_0">macaikido@yahoo.com</span> or call 890-1976 (Marlene or Barbi).<br><br><br>* Getting there:<br><br>A) DRIVING YOUR CAR<br><br></span></font><small><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Club
650 is on the right coming from the south (Makati/The Fort etc), beside
Shopwise and before the entrance to Eastwood. Coming from the the north
(UP/Ateneo/Blue Ridge area), take C-5 into Libis area and make a u-turn
a few hundred meters after the Jollibee/Delifrance outlet. There is
ample parking in front.</span><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"></small><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><br>B) USING PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION<br><br></span></font><small><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Club
650 is accessible via the jeeps that traverse C-5. From EDSA, get off
at the Ortigas intersection, take a jeep to the Ortigas-C-5
intersection, get off at C-5 and take a second jeep north towards
Eastwood. Club 650 will be on the right coming from the south</span><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">
(Makati), beside Shopwise and before the entrance to Eastwood.</span></small><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><br><br>Nothing follows.</span></font><small><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br></span><br></span></small><p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font color="#3300cc" face="Arial,Helvetica,Univers,Zurich BT" size="-1"><span style="color: white;">.</span></font></p><h3 style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font style="font-weight: normal;" color="#3300cc" face="Arial,Helvetica,Univers,Zurich BT" size="-1"><a href="106thFFA.html">back
to top &gt;&gt;&gt;</a></font><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: 400;"><i><span style="font-style: italic;">&nbsp;</span></i></span></font></h3><p style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font color="#3300cc" face="Arial,Helvetica,Univers,Zurich BT" size="-1"><span style="color: white;">*************************************************************************************************************</span></font></p></td></tr><tr><td style="white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: top;"></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>&nbsp;
